PERSONAL USE — FREE AND UNRESTRICTED

You are free to use Sigillerie and its outputs for personal use, including:
- Studying, research, and education
- Creating things for yourself
- Writing articles, blog posts, social-media content
- Side projects and personal experiments
- Personal portfolio or showcase work

No request needed. Use it.

COMMERCIAL USE — REQUIRES WRITTEN AUTHORIZATION

Any company, team, or for-profit organization integrating this skill into a
product, external service, or client deliverable must obtain written
authorization from the maintainer first. This includes but is not limited to:

- Using the skill as part of internal company tooling
- Using skill outputs as the primary creative method for external deliverables
- Building a commercial product on top of the skill
- Using the skill in paid client projects
- Embedding generated assets into commercial properties without separate
  asset-level licensing

Commercial licensing contact: github.com/realsammyt (DM via GitHub).

THIRD-PARTY ASSETS

Sigillerie is designed to generate audio assets through external services
such as Stability AI (Stable Audio) and ElevenLabs Sound Effects. No audio
assets ship with this repository. Assets you generate are governed by the
license tier of your own API keys; treat them as personal-use prototyping
material unless your tier permits commercial output. Record license metadata
for each generated asset in a license-trail.md sidecar next to the assets
(format: capabilities/generative-audio/anti-patterns.md, License Trail Break
entry) and keep it with the assets for audit purposes.

